sleepingoverhaul.config.Restrictions.allowSleepDuringDay=Sleep during day?
sleepingoverhaul.config.Restrictions.allowSleepDuringDay.tooltip=If true, players can sleep during the day and will NOT be automatically woken-up either.
sleepingoverhaul.config.Restrictions.sleepAnywhere=[CMC] Sleep anywhere?
sleepingoverhaul.config.Restrictions.sleepAnywhere.tooltip=REQUIRES CMC. If true, unlocks sleeping ability in any dimension (e.g. Nether).\nNote #1: Respawn point will not be reset, you always respawn in overworld.\nNote #2: Other dimensions have their own idea about night-time, e.g. Nether is always night.



