sleepingoverhaul.config.TimelapseMode.rate=Timelapse max TPS
sleepingoverhaul.config.TimelapseMode.rate.tooltip=Maximum tickrate for Timelapse.\nNote that Tickrate Changer will throttle back tickrate as necessary to avoid total CPU saturation.



