sleepingoverhaul.config.SleepVote=Sleep-vote Configuration
sleepingoverhaul.config.SleepVote.tooltip=Configuration options related to the sleep vote system.
sleepingoverhaul.config.SleepVote.percent=Sleep Vote percent
sleepingoverhaul.config.SleepVote.percent.tooltip=Minimum percent of players required before sleep vote reminders (and actions, if any) can occur.
sleepingoverhaul.config.SleepVote.actionTimeout=Vote Action timeout
sleepingoverhaul.config.SleepVote.actionTimeout.tooltip=Once the percentage of sleeping players is reached, wait this many seconds before performing the configured vote action.\nNote that if the sleeping player percentage drops below the configured minimum, the timeout action is cancelled.
sleepingoverhaul.config.SleepVote.action=Vote Action selection
sleepingoverhaul.config.SleepVote.action.tooltip=The action to perform once actionTimeout has elapsed (assuming the sleeping player percentage has been maintained).\n    NONE: Take no action, just show the reminder.\n    TIMELAPSE_ANYWAY: Continue with Timelapse - awake players have to deal with the server tickrate being sped-up.\n    CMC_KICK_AWAKE: Requires CMC (otherwise skip-to-day will occur after kick). Kick awake players, then continue with Timelapse.\n    SKIP_TO_DAY: Skip to the next day (fallback to vanilla Minecraft behavior).
sleepingoverhaul.config.SleepVote.reminderText=Sleeping reminder text
sleepingoverhaul.config.SleepVote.reminderText.tooltip=Text that will be periodically displayed to other players when the configured percent has been reached.\n(COUNT) will be replaced with (e.g.) '2/3' to display currently-sleeping/total players.\n(COUNT) will be replaced with remaining time before sleep action is performed.
sleepingoverhaul.config.SleepVote.reminderTextDisplayTime=Sleeping reminder time
sleepingoverhaul.config.SleepVote.reminderTextDisplayTime.tooltip=How many seconds at a time to display a reminder to players.
sleepingoverhaul.config.SleepVote.reminderTextRepeatTime=Sleeping reminder interval
sleepingoverhaul.config.SleepVote.reminderTextRepeatTime.tooltip=How many seconds between successive reminder displays.

sleepingoverhaul.config.SleepVote.allAsleepText=All-asleep text
sleepingoverhaul.config.SleepVote.allAsleepText.tooltip=Text displayed when all players are asleep.
sleepingoverhaul.config.SleepVote.votePassedText=Vote-passed text
sleepingoverhaul.config.SleepVote.votePassedText.tooltip=Text displayed when vote action has passed.

sleepingoverhaul.config.SleepVote.cancelledText=Action cancelled text
sleepingoverhaul.config.SleepVote.cancelledText.tooltip=Text to display to players when an active or pending vote action is cancelled for whatever reason.\n(COUNT) will be replaced with (e.g.) '2/3' to display currently-sleeping/total players.

sleepingoverhaul.config.SleepVote.kickedText=Action kicked text
sleepingoverhaul.config.SleepVote.kickedText.tooltip=Text to display to players (The 'Reason' on the Disconnected screen) when they're kicked as the result of a vote. Note that due to a Minecraft bug, sometimes a generic reason may still show instead.